sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Orch as Orchestrator<br/>8033/TCP HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Optional TLS/mTLS
    participant Chunker as Chunker Service<br/>8085/TCP gRPC<br/>Optional TLS/mTLS
    participant Detector as Detector Service(s)<br/>8080/TCP HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Optional TLS/mTLS
    participant GenSrv as Generation Server<br/>(TGIS/NLP/OpenAI)
    participant OTEL as OTLP Collector<br/>4317/TCP gRPC

    Note over Client,GenSrv: Flow 1: Unary Text Generation with Detection (v1)

    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v1/task/classification-with-text-generation<br/>Optional mTLS client cert
    Orch->>OTEL: Trace span start (traceparent)
    Orch->>Chunker: ChunkerTokenizationTaskPredict (input text)<br/>gRPC, Optional mTLS
    Chunker-->>Orch: Chunked input tokens
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents (input detection)<br/>Optional Bearer token
    Detector-->>Orch: Detection results (input)
    Note over Orch: Check input detections against thresholds
    Orch->>GenSrv: Generate RPC / POST /v1/completions<br/>gRPC or HTTP, Optional TLS/mTLS
    GenSrv-->>Orch: Generated text
    Orch->>Chunker: ChunkerTokenizationTaskPredict (output text)<br/>gRPC, Optional mTLS
    Chunker-->>Orch: Chunked output tokens
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/generation (output detection)<br/>Optional Bearer token
    Detector-->>Orch: Detection results (output)
    Note over Orch: Check output detections against thresholds
    Orch->>OTEL: Trace span end + metrics
    Orch-->>Client: JSON response with text + detections

    Note over Client,GenSrv: Flow 2: Streaming Chat Completions with Detection (v2)

    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>Optional mTLS client cert
    Orch->>OTEL: Trace span start (traceparent)
    Orch->>Chunker: ChunkerTokenizationTaskPredict (input messages)<br/>gRPC, Optional mTLS
    Chunker-->>Orch: Chunked input
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/chat (input detection)<br/>Optional Bearer token
    Detector-->>Orch: Input detection results
    Orch->>GenSrv: POST /v1/chat/completions (stream=true)<br/>HTTP/HTTPS SSE, Optional Bearer
    loop Streaming tokens
        GenSrv-->>Orch: SSE token chunk
        Orch->>Chunker: BidiStreamingChunkerTokenizationTaskPredict<br/>gRPC bidirectional streaming
        Chunker-->>Orch: Output chunk
        Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/generation (chunk detection)<br/>Optional Bearer token
        Detector-->>Orch: Chunk detection results
        Note over Orch: DetectionBatcherManager aggregates<br/>concurrent detection results via mpsc
        Orch-->>Client: SSE response chunk with detections
    end
    Orch->>OTEL: Trace span end + metrics
    Orch-->>Client: SSE stream complete

    Note over Client,GenSrv: Flow 3: Standalone Content Detection (v2)

    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v2/text/detection/content<br/>Optional mTLS client cert
    Orch->>Chunker: ChunkerTokenizationTaskPredict<br/>gRPC, Optional mTLS
    Chunker-->>Orch: Chunked text
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>Optional Bearer token
    Detector-->>Orch: Detection results
    Orch-->>Client: JSON detection response
